C4Context
    title Weather Notification Application - System Context

    Person(user, "User", "Receives weather updates and notifications")

    System(weatherApp, "Weather Notification App", "Fetches weather data and sends notifications")

    System_Ext(weatherAPI, "Weather API (OpenWeatherMap)", "Provides real-time weather data")

    System_Ext(notificationService, "Notification Service (Push/SMS/Email)", "Delivers weather alerts to users")

    System_Ext(authService, "Authentication Service (Firebase Auth/OAuth)", "Handles user authentication")

    user -> weatherApp : Uses
    weatherApp -> weatherAPI : Fetches weather data
    weatherApp -> notificationService : Sends alerts
    user -> authService : Logs in / Registers
    weatherApp -> authService : Validates user identity
